WEBVTT

00:02.869 --> 00:05.905
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:05.905 --> 00:07.624
DEEJAY: ...of J.J. Mikes. (whistling)

00:07.624 --> 00:08.992
Party till dawn on the Big W.

00:08.992 --> 00:11.294
WOMAN (over radio):
Tired of your old job?

00:11.294 --> 00:13.797
Looking for something new and exciting?

00:13.797 --> 00:16.299
Then how about a career
as a court stenographer?

00:16.299 --> 00:18.301
Through a simple six-week course

00:18.301 --> 00:20.303
at the Emory School
of Court Stenography,

00:20.303 --> 00:22.305
you'll learn all the skills required

00:22.305 --> 00:24.808
to become part of this
exciting profession.

00:24.808 --> 00:27.761
Meet great people, work flexible hours,

00:27.761 --> 00:29.763
earn top money.

00:29.763 --> 00:32.766
All it takes is a good
ear, accuracy and speed.

00:32.766 --> 00:35.268
Contact the Emory School
of Court Stenography

00:35.769 --> 00:37.153
for your free aptitude test

00:37.153 --> 00:41.107
by calling
5-double-5-6-1-1-9.

00:41.107 --> 00:43.109
That number again:

00:43.109 --> 00:45.111
5-double-five-6-1-1-9.

00:45.111 --> 00:46.613
Don't delay. 5...

00:46.613 --> 00:49.032
To have an exciting career
in court stenography,

00:49.032 --> 00:53.536
just call
5-double-5-6-1-1-9,

00:53.536 --> 00:56.005
now.
5-5-5-6...

00:56.005 --> 01:01.344
DEEJAY: You're listening to the
rockin' sounds of J.J. Mikes.

01:01.845 --> 01:07.350
But first, let's take a look at
tomorrow's weather... (Woody whistling)

01:07.350 --> 01:11.221
(piano plays)

01:11.221 --> 01:13.690
? Making your way in the world today ?

01:13.690 --> 01:16.693
? Takes everything you've got ?

01:16.693 --> 01:19.696
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

01:19.696 --> 01:22.699
? Sure would help a lot ?

01:23.199 --> 01:27.954
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

01:27.954 --> 01:30.740
? Sometimes you want to go ?

01:30.740 --> 01:36.246
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:36.246 --> 01:40.750
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:40.750 --> 01:43.253
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:43.253 --> 01:45.755
? Our troubles are all the same ?

01:45.755 --> 01:51.261
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

01:51.261 --> 01:53.763
? You want to go where people know ?

01:53.763 --> 01:56.266
? People are all the same ?

01:56.266 --> 02:00.770
? You want to go where
everybody knows your name. ?

